11-json web token-to auhenticate request
    -install jsonwebtoken:npm i jsonwebtoken
    -Import jsonwebtoken i dataservice.js
    -to generate token when login success-sign()
    -we have to send the token to client
    -client will sent token along with request after login
    -verify token which is avilable in index.js
      -import json webtoken in index.js
      -verify the token-verify() before resolving client request
